import React from "react";
import {
  Box, Grid, Card, Typography, Avatar, Button, Divider
} from "@mui/material";
import ShoppingCartIcon from "@mui/icons-material/ShoppingCart";
import WalletIcon from "@mui/icons-material/AccountBalanceWallet";
import StarIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Star";

const UserDashboard = () => (
  <Box sx={{
    bgcolor: "#fff5f7",
    minHeight: "100vh",
    py: 0,
    width: "100vw", // Full width for laptop screens
  }}>
    {/* Header */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        bgcolor: "#e23744",
        color: "#fff",
        py: 4,
        px: 6,
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 30,
        borderBottomRightRadius: 30,
        mb: 8,
        boxShadow: 2,
        display: "flex",
        alignItems: "center",
        justifyContent: "space-between",
        width: "100%",
        maxWidth: "none",
        minHeight: 125
      }}
    >
      <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
        <Avatar
          sx={{
            width: 72,
            height: 72,
            bgcolor: "#fff",
            color: "#e23744",
            fontWeight: 700,
            fontSize: 32,
            mr: 3
          }}
        >
          U
        </Avatar>
        <Box>
          <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={900} sx={{ letterSpacing: 1 }}>
            Welcome, [User Name]!
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight={500} sx={{ opacity: .92 }}>
            Doorstep fuel delivery, made easy.
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Box>
      <Button
        variant="contained"
        sx={{
          bgcolor: "#fff",
          color: "#e23744",
          fontWeight: 700,
          borderRadius: 99,
          px: 5,
          py: 1.3,
          boxShadow: 1,
          fontSize: 18,
          '&:hover': { bgcolor: "#ffb0b9" }
        }}
      >
        MY ACCOUNT
      </Button>
    </Box>
    {/* Dashboard Cards */}
    <Box maxWidth="1200px" mx="auto">
      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        {/* Loyalty */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{
            p: 3.5,
            borderRadius: 3,
            boxShadow: 4,
            minHeight: 110,
            display: "flex",
            alignItems: "center",
            bgcolor: "#fff"
          }}>
            <StarIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 48, mr: 2 }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight={700} sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>
                Available Loyalty
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={900}>₹0</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        {/* Wallet */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{
            p: 3.5,
            borderRadius: 3,
            boxShadow: 4,
            minHeight: 110,
            display: "flex",
            alignItems: "center",
            bgcolor: "#fff"
          }}>
            <WalletIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 48, mr: 2 }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight={700} sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>
                My Wallet Limit
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={900}>₹0</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        {/* Cart */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{
            p: 3.5,
            borderRadius: 3,
            boxShadow: 4,
            minHeight: 110,
            display: "flex",
            alignItems: "center",
            bgcolor: "#fff"
          }}>
            <ShoppingCartIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 48, mr: 2 }} />
            <Box>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight={700} sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>
                Cart Status
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={900}>Active</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      {/* Orders and Assets */}
      <Divider sx={{ my: 6 }} />
      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        {/* Last 5 Orders */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
          <Card sx={{
            borderRadius: 3,
            boxShadow: 4,
            p: 4,
            bgcolor: "#fff",
            minHeight: 200,
            display: "flex",
            flexDirection: "column"
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={900} mb={1} sx={{ letterSpacing: 1, color: "#e23744" }}>
              My Last 5 Orders
            </Typography>
            <Divider sx={{ mb: 2 }} />
            <Typography sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>No records found</Typography>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        {/* Assets */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card sx={{
            borderRadius: 3,
            boxShadow: 4,
            p: 4,
            bgcolor: "#fff",
            minHeight: 200,
            display: "flex",
            flexDirection: "column"
          }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={900} mb={1} sx={{ letterSpacing: 1, color: "#e23744" }}>
              My Assets
            </Typography>
            <Divider sx={{ mb: 2 }} />
            <Typography sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>No records found</Typography>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  </Box>
);

export default UserDashboard;
